The last `sorry` is in the proof of `marcinkiewicz_zygmund_symmetric` theorem, in the last calculation step. The goal is to show that `‚ąę ŌČ, (‚ąŹ i ‚ąą A, ‚ÄĖX i ŌČ‚ÄĖ ^ (2 * w i)) ‚ąāőľ` equals `marcinkiewiczZygmundSymmConst (2 * m) * ‚ąę ŌČ, (‚ąĎ i ‚ąą A, ‚ÄĖX i ŌČ‚ÄĖ ^ 2) ^ m ‚ąāőľ`.

