        -- number of times in `I`.
        _ = ‚ąę ŌČ, -‚ąŹ k, inner ‚ĄĚ (X (I k).1 ŌČ) (X (I k).2 ŌČ) ‚ąāőľ := by
          congr with ŌČ
          calc
