    _ = marcinkiewiczZygmundSymmConst (2 * m) * ‚ąę ŌČ, (‚ąĎ i ‚ąą A, ‚ÄĖX i ŌČ‚ÄĖ ^ 2) ^ m ‚ąāőľ := by
      simp_rw [sum_pow_eq_sum_piAntidiag, ‚Üź pow_mul, ‚Üź integral_const_mul, mul_sum, ‚Üź mul_assoc]
      rw [integral_finset_sum]
      rintro w hw
      exact .const_mul sorry _
```

This completes the proof by showing that the sum is equal to the desired expression. The final step involves simplifying the sum over the antidiagonal and using the fact that the sum of the weights is equal to $m$.
